beraus großzügigen Schenkung knapp dreißig Blätter der Albertina vermacht. Aus diesem Anlass entstehen eine Ausstellung und diese Publikation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aART / History / General.2bisacsh  aRestitution, Nationalsozialismus, Arthur Feldmann, Provenienzforschung.1 aEßl, Julia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGnann, Achim, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPichler, Martina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchödl, Heinz, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2015z9783110438642oZDB-23-DKA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783205201571423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783205201571.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKAb2015